msgid ""
"Dark times await Idaamub. After a long period of peace between races, orcs "
"have begun to attack peasant villages. But, in the shadows, a dark presence "
"pulls the strings. Travel through Idaamub to prevent it from falling into "
"chaos."
msgstr ""

