#. [side], type=Trapper
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:445
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\23_Abxoowbus_Trading_Post.cfg:330
msgid "Merchants"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:472
msgid "Well, it looks like the secret entrance is in a house on the other side."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:476
msgid "And outside more orcs."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:480
msgid "What a surprise."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:488
msgid ""
"Wait! It looks like a few dwarves are getting attacked by the orcs! We need "
"to save them!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:529
msgid ""
"East: Zei\n"
"South: Qyizu, Udxatfe\n"
"North-west: Uvju’s Cross, western tower"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:554
msgid ""
"It looks like the door is blocked by rocks. There's a barrel full of powder "
"next to them. Should I light it up?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:556
msgid "Yes but be careful not to get hurt."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:576
msgid ""
"The blast was more powerful than I expected. I don't think it is possible to "
"light those barrels up without being hurt by the explosion."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:582
msgid "No, it's too dangerous."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:601
msgid "The door is now cleared. Should I open it?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:603
msgid "Yes, let's open the pass back."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:612
msgid "The door is open."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:618
msgid "No, wait a bit."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:637
msgid "Well, we were trying to find a way to open this door."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:641
msgid ""
"You must be the reckless farmer my guards talk to me about. I wouldn’t ’ve "
"believed it if I hadn’t seen it with my own eyes."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:645
msgid "Tell me, have you really killed all these orcs?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:649
msgid "Yes, we did."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:653
msgid ""
"Zei is hugely indebted to you, pal. We will do our best to keep the lands "
"you’ve conquered for us."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Aeraent
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:664
msgid "Here is a little reward for having opened the door."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:668
msgid "Thank you, sir."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:688
msgid ""
"West: Qyizu's mines, Udxatfe\n"
"South-east: Zei"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:712
msgid ""
"Wuz crackalackin'. If you wanna git all up in Zei, itz pointless. I heard tha"
" city was burnt some nights ago."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:717
msgid ""
"We is thinin bout tha way we is goin ta feed our mulez until tha arrival of "
"our associates. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:722
msgid "To drop a rhyme tha real deal, one mule should be enough now, nahmeean?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:726
msgid "I have no idea what he just said. I think he is trying to sell us a mule."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:748
msgid "D-ya want a mule? Fo` 10 gold keep'n it real yo?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:750
msgid "I'm sorry my brave, but we don't need a mule."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:755
msgid "As yo ass wish."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:762
msgid "Hello, mah brave. We wizzould indee' be interested 'n a M-to-tha-izzule."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:777
msgid ""
"I be S-O-Double-Rizzy, bizzy yizzy dizzy have enizzle monizzle (You do not "
"have enough gold)."
msgstr ""

#. [unit], id=Darl'n, type=Bay Horse
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:788
msgid "Darl'n"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:797
msgid "Hizzere is. What her nizzle?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Giles
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:802
msgid "She be Darl'n. I hizzle she will sizzy you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:840
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:983
msgid "It’s a rough job, but we must live. Besides, we’re not the only ones…"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:850
msgid "I'm sorry we couldn't save more of you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:856
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:999
msgid "What were those orcs doing here?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:860
msgid ""
"They were looking for magical items. And where do you think the magical items"
" the orcs are stealing go? They end up in the pocket of a Commander Isut."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:864
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1007
msgid "May I be turn into a mule if there is no goblin in all this! "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:868
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1011
msgid "You seem to know a lot about what is happening."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:872
msgid ""
"My brother Hufifa must know more but the orcs locked him up down there. I "
"would need your help to free him if you agree."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:876
msgid ""
"I'm sorry, but we need to reach Udxatfe as fast as possible. We don't have "
"the time to enter the mine to look for your brother."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:881
msgid ""
"Don't worry. The way to Udxatfe is through the lower level of the mine. "
"That's where my brother is locked. I will show you the way."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:883
msgid "Sure, we will help you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:898
msgid ""
"Charge! There are some twenty orcs down there to whom we shall teach some "
"manners!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:902
msgid "You can now recruit dwarvish fighters."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:907
msgid "No, it is too dangerous. We'd rather have you to stay here."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:911
msgid "You understand nothing! "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:915
msgid "We are at war right now. Against whom or against what, nobody knows!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Amin
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:919
msgid ""
"So, if you think you can get out of it all by yourself, go on, don’t "
"hesitate!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:993
msgid "I'm sorry when couldn't save more of you."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1003
msgid ""
"They were looking for magical items. And where do you think go the magical "
"items the orcs are stealing? They end in the pocket of a Commander Isut. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1015
msgid "Hufifa must know more but the orcs locked him up down there."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1019
msgid ""
"I'm sorry, but we need to reach Udxatfe as fast as possible. We don't have "
"the time to enter the mine to look for your friend."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1023
msgid ""
"Don't worry. The way to Udxatfe is through the lower level of the mine. "
"That's where Hufifa is locked"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1061
msgid "Well, it looks like we must cross the mines to reach Udxatfe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1065
msgid "We will try to find and save Hufifa on the way."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1069
msgid "He might have valuable information about what is happening."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Raffolk
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1081
msgid "Well, this is where I leave you. See you around."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1108
msgid "The events are too serious that you can continue without a leader."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1118
msgid "I need to go back to Zei and find a way to reopen Yooradweak's pass."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Csia
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1122
msgid "For the sake of all of us, I hope you will find Teumiuxe alive."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=narrator
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1146
msgid "You can no longer recruit nor recall Sergeants."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=second_unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1190
msgid "That's it. The dwarves should be safe."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1216
msgid ""
"The dwarves are all dead! How can we imagine saving the country if we can't "
"even save a few persons?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Io
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1247
msgid ""
"The dwarves have suffered enough. We won't accept gold from them. Only food "
"and rest."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1261
msgid "My good friend! Our meeting is certainly a sign of fate."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1265
msgid ""
"I need some items to bring them to my… hmmm… commercial partners… and you "
"totally look like you have some."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=unit
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1269
msgid "Well, we collected some items during our journey."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1273
msgid ""
"Yes, truly, you have what I need. Would you consent selling me some in "
"exchange for a substantial sum?"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=trader
#: .\scenarios\chapter2\11_Qyizu.cfg:1311
msgid "I notably look for magic goods. If you have some, of course."
msgstr ""

