#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1919
#: .\utils\item_list.cfg:8857
msgid "Potion of rejuvenation"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1826
msgid "I'm Eukhac, the best bowwoman of Idaamub."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1841
msgid "I am ruined, fully ruined!"
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1845
msgid ""
"During six years, all my money and all my efforts went into the preparation "
"of the contest of best bowman of the known lands. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1849
msgid ""
"But the day right before the contest, catastrophe! Our funds were stolen by "
"the goblins! Our prizes were stolen! "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1853
msgid "I only have my bow and my talent left to try to save my stained reputation."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1857
msgid ""
"I followed the goblins down to here, but I can’t go any further as I ain’t "
"got a dime to buy food. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1876
msgid ""
"If you have a bit of gold for me, I would be glad to help you. That way, I "
"would continue looking for my stolen treasure in good company."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1880
msgid "I would need 38400 gold to reimburse the Travellers and buy some food."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1884
msgid "Can you help me?"
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1886
msgid "Yes, we can."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1896
msgid "I am afraid you don't have enough gold to help me."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1940
msgid ""
"The bow and honor of Eukhac are yours, my good friend. I am glad to follow "
"you."
msgstr ""

#. [option]
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1953
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\32_Eastern_Swamp.cfg:1161
#: .\scenarios\chapter5\38_Isut.cfg:853
msgid "Sorry, we don't have enough gold."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1957
msgid "Please excuse me for my straightforward request. "
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1961
msgid "I should have seen that your funds are in the same state as mines."
msgstr ""

#. [message], speaker=Eukhac
#: .\scenarios\chapter4\28_Travelers.cfg:1965
msgid "Farewell, then, and may luck be in your favor."
msgstr ""

