#. [part]
#: .\utils\intro.cfg:4
msgid ""
"A long time ago, on the Great Continent, the Empire of Stars, beacon of "
"civilization, fell into oblivion. Its powerthirsty legions and an old and "
"pitiless spirit put an end to it."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: .\utils\intro.cfg:8
msgid ""
"The 10th Legion, jewel of the military, composed of the bravest and most "
"trustworthy soldiers of this falling empire, retired far east to a land named"
" Idaamub. On this welcoming land, the 10th Legion tried to preserve what the "
"empire had lost."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: .\utils\intro.cfg:12
msgid ""
"It is here, between those wild mountains and rich vales that the 10th Legion "
"settled. That’s the way the kingdom of Idaamub was founded, prosperous, free "
"and peaceful for more than 300 years. Humans were at peace with the other "
"races, orcs and goblins included."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: .\utils\intro.cfg:16
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, the peace had a prize. Few are those who remember the evil "
"spirit that opposed them. Fewer are those who could remember the spells that "
"could save them."
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: .\utils\intro.cfg:20
msgid ""
"And no one could have predicted that a peaceful farmer would be torn between "
"a revenge from the past and the survival of a kingdom."
msgstr ""

